  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Cut Reeds/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Cut Reeds</b> are an item obtained by harvesting <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reeds\" title=\"Reeds\">Reeds</a> that grow in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Swamp\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Swamp\">Swamps</a>. Reeds can be refined into <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\">Papyrus</a> and are a crafting ingredient for a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blow_Dart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Blow Dart\">Blow Dart</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sleep_Dart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sleep Dart\">Sleep Dart</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Dart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fire Dart\">Fire Dart</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pan_Flute\" title=\"Pan Flute\">Pan Flute</a>. Reeds grow back after 3 days from being picked, but they will not grow in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Winter\">Winter</a>.\n</p><p>There is an alternative method of obtaining Cut Reeds: by destroying <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweeds</a>. There is a 1% chance of it dropping from the 3 possible drops. Also, a friendly <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Catcoon\" title=\"Catcoon\">Catcoon</a> can gift the player Cut Reeds.\n</p><p>Reeds can also be harvested from the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rocky_Beach\" title=\"Rocky Beach\">Rocky Beach</a> biome on the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Island\" title=\"Lunar Island\">Lunar Island</a>.\n</p><p><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monkeytails\" title=\"Monkeytails\">Monkeytails</a> are another source of Cut Reeds that can be transplanted near one&#x27;s base for easy harvesting.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Reeds\" title=\"Cut Reeds\"><img alt=\"Cut Reeds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cut_Reeds.png?1ce430\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\"><img alt=\"Papyrus.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Papyrus.png?5e1602\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Reeds\" title=\"Cut Reeds\"><img alt=\"Cut Reeds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cut_Reeds.png?1ce430\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rope\" title=\"Rope\"><img alt=\"Rope.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Rope.png?41fbab\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prestihatitator\" title=\"Prestihatitator\"><img alt=\"Prestihatitator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prestihatitator.png/42px-Pres