  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|image = Cut Reeds Dropped.png\n|icon = Cut Reeds.png\n|foodType = Roughage [[File:Roughage.png|32px|link=Roughage]]<br>(non-survivor food)\n|hpRestored     = 1\n|hungerRestored = 4.7\n|sanityRestored = 0\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 15 sec.\n|stack = 40\n|droppedBy = {{Pic24|Reeds}}, {{Pic24|Monkeytails}}\n|craft_desctiption =''Tubular.''\n|crafting_text = {{Pic32|Ash}}x4 \n|tier_text = {{Pic32|Wandering Trader}}\n|filter      = {{Pic32|Trading Filter}}\n|spawnCode = \"cutreeds\"\n|canBeBurned=1}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Cut reeds, ready for crafting and hobbying.\n|willow = Cut reeds, ready for burning. Or maybe crafting.\n|wolfgang = I made a clump of reeds.\n|wendy = I like to cut things up.\n|wx78 = HOLLOW PLANT MATTER\n|wickerbottom = Some rush cuttings.\n|woodie = Want to hear my loon call?\n|maxwell = I think I could build something useful from this.\n|wagstaff = Pliable yet tough. Very useful. Very useful indeed.\n|wigfrid = I cleaned all the bugs öut! Then I ate them.\n|webber = Reeds, web, what's the difference.\n|walani = It was hard work cutting those. Nap time!\n|warly = Smells like greenery.\n|woodlegs = But Woodlegs can't reed.\n|wilba = 'TIS REEDS\n|wormwood = Hair cut\n|wheeler = Only useful in twos or threes. Or fours or fives.\n|winona = Doesn't hold a candle to steel pipe.\n|wortox = One swift yank was all it took.\n|wurt = Swamp full of useful things, florp.\n|walter = Ms. Wickerbottom might need some more... reed-ing material.\n|wanda = I'll put it in my pocket and use it for something later.\n|choose = wurt}}\n'''Cut Reeds''' are an item obtained by harvesting [[Reeds]] that grow in [[Swamp]]s. Reeds can be refined into [[Papyrus]] and are a crafting ingredient for a [[Blow Dart]], [[Sleep Dart]], [[Fire Dart]] and [[Pan Flute]]. Reeds grow back after 3 days from being picked, but they will not grow in [[Winter]].\n\nThere is an alternative method of obtaining Cut Reeds: by destroying [[Tumbleweed]]s. There is a 1% chance of it dropping from the 3 possible drops. Also, a friendly [[Catcoon]] can gift the player Cut Reeds.\n\nReeds can also be harvested from the [[Rocky Beach]] biome on the [[Lunar Island]].\n\n[[Monkeytails]] are another source of Cut Reeds that can be transplanted near one's base for easy harvesting.\n\n=={{Pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 4\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Papyrus}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Rope\n|item3 = Mandrake\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Pan Flute}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Hound's Tooth\n|item3 = Azure Feather\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Blow Dart}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Stinger\n|item3 = Crow Feather\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Sleep Dart}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Charcoal\n|item3 = Crimson Feather\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Fire Dart}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Gold Nugget\n|item3 = Saffron Feather\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Electric Dart}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Down Feather\n|count2 = 5\n|item3 = Rope\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Luxury Fan}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Carrot\n|count2 = 4\n|tool = Benevolent Rabbit King\n|result = Burrowing Horn}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Cave Banana\n|item3 = Health Decrease\n|count3 = 15\n|result = Monkeytails Tuft Dug\n|character = Wormwood\n|skill = Monkeytail Crafting}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Freshwater Fish\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Boards\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Craftsmerm House\n|character = Wurt}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|item2 = Rot\n|count2 = 2\n|result = Marsh Turf\n|resultcount = 4\n|character = Wurt}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|item2 = Rot\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Terra Firma Tamper\n|result = Marsh Turf\n|resultcount = 4}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|item2 = Freshwater Fish\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|result = Clever Disguise\n|character = Wurt}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Boards\n|count2 = 2\n|result = Communal Kelp Dish\n|character = Wurt\n|skill = Community Feeder I}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Cut Reeds\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Boards\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Tentacle Spots\n|count3 = 1\n|result = Superior Communal Kelp Dish\n|skill = Community Feeder II}}\n\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nCD cutreeds.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\n</gallery>\n\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nFood=\n{{Food}}\n</tabber>\n[[fr:Roseaux coupés]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]"
